high_descs: Turn right and head to the dishwasher.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Go slightly right to the bread on the counter.
Cut the bread on the counter.
Go to the microwave above the counter.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Go back to the bread below the microwave.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Go back to the microwave.
Warm up the bread in the microwave and pick it back up.
Turn right, go to the end of the counter and turn left to face the shelf.
Put the slice of bread on the shelf to the right of the glass.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm slice of bread on the shelf.

high_descs: Walk forward and to the right to face the left end of the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Take a step to the right to face the bread on the counter.
Cut the bread on the counter into slices.
Look up to face the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Look down to face the bread on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Look up to face the microwave.
Heat the bread in the microwave and remove it.
Step right and look up to face the back of the counter.
Place the bread slice on the back of the counter.
anns.task_desc: To heat a bread slice plus place it on the back of the counter to the right of the stove.

high_descs: Turn right, walk until you reach the counter, then turn left and walk until you hit the dishwasher
Pick up the knife from the counter
Turn right, walk forward a step, then turn left to face the counter
Cut six slices from the loaf of bread.
Turn left, walk forward a step,  then turn right to face the microwave
Open the microwave and place the knife inside
Close the door and turn on the microwave, then turn left, take a step forward and turn right to face the loaf of bread
Pick up a slice of bread
Turn left, walk forward a step and turn right to face the microwave
Place the bread in the microwave on the plate, close the door and turn on the microwave, wait a few seconds, then remove the bread
Turn right, walk forward till you hit the counter, then turn left
Place the bread on the shelf between the glass and the knife
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of heated bread on a shelf
